en_2754328_0	Colombo (News 1st): Police say statements from more than 40 people have been recorded in connection with the abduction and murder of 2 businessmen in Rathgama.
en_2754328_1	Police Media Spokesperson, SP Ruwan Gunasekara said, there are police officials and relatives of the two victims, among those who provided statements.
en_2754328_2	SP Gunasekara also noted that the 5 police constables who went missing are yet to appear before the CID.
en_2754328_3	Charges have been leveled against the Southern Provincial Special Investigation Unit over the abduction and murder of two businessmen from Rathgama.
